I '''Mar Shimun XXI Benyamin''' ([[Syriac language|Syriac]]: ܡܪܝ ܒܢܝܡܝܢ ܫܡܥܘܢ ܥܣܪܝܢ ܘܩܕܡܝܐ) metung yang [[Catholicos]] [[Patriarch]] ning  [[w:Assyrian Church of the East]]. Mibait ya kanitang [[1887]]  king barriu ning [[Qochanis]] king  [[w:Hakkari Province|lalawigan ning Hakkari]], [[w:Ottoman Empire]] (modern-day southeastern [[Turkey]]).  Melalang yang [[w:Metropolitan bishop|Metropolitan]] kanitang [[w:March 16]], [[1903]] kapamilatan nang  [[Mar Rowil]], the Catholicos Patriarch a mete anyang [[w:March 16]], [[1903]]. Diciochu ya edad anyang elilan ne itang minunang makalukluk, at melwat yang labinglimang (15) banwa king [[w:Episcopal see|patriarchal See]] ning [[Seleucia-Ctesiphon]] king Qudchanis. Anyang Marzo ning [[1918]], pete ne ning metung a armadung grupung (paramilitary group) [[w:Kurdish people|Kurdish]] lalam ning bandera ning [[w:truce|pamituknang akbung]] (lon me ing [[Assyrian Genocide]]).

==Simbitla (Quotes)==
*"E ku malyaring sumuku at pati na ing kanakung balen kaybat kung asaksian ing eganaganang karokan a mengapalyari kareng kanakung kabangsang Assyrian. Uli na niti, metung ya mu ing kanakung kapatad, at dakal la reng kanakung memalen. Burian ku pa ing mawala ya kanaku ing kanakung kapatad kesa king kanakung balen. " 
